- Empty or placeholder: Section 1 indications and manufacturer, Section 3
  regulatory status, Section 4 raw materials + composition, Section 5
  equipment, Section 6 process narrative, Section 7 process flow,
  Section 8 Loratadine spec, Section 9 patent status, Section 12
